Ms. Sung, we have a situation!

5
00:01:44,312 --> 00:01:45,188
What is it?

6
00:01:45,271 --> 00:01:47,482
The plane got delayed,
so it just got handed over to customs.

7
00:01:49,567 --> 00:01:51,528
-When is it expected to arrive?
-At seven.

8
00:01:51,653 --> 00:01:54,656
